caption:
We’ve got a crispy little tip for your next taco night! For the *crrrrunchiest* experience with our NEW Maíz Corn Taco Shells, we recommend baking them at 375°F for a **minimum of 5 minutes**. 

If you like your shells extra toasty, you can leave them in for an additional 1–2 minutes—just keep a close eye on them so they don’t overcook. ¡Buen provecho! ❤️
